metadata.name: Crypt O's NFT Crunch Cereal
metadata.description:
Crypt O's NFT Crunch cereal was made for the common gmer, mfer, and degenerate NFT collector. Every bite is filled with the hope, love, and heartbreak that we have all endured in Web3 together.

No need to worry any longer, we heard you! With the newest addition of Kevin, we aimed to balance the hope and love with a little more heartbreak. So go ahead, buy the top and sell the bottom... each rug hurts a little less after a delicious bowl of Crypt O's NFT Crunch: The best way to say gm!
